creator: Kahunasio
descriptionHtml:
Online fitness coaching.

Includes daily support, weekly check-ins done by video feedback

Nutrition Plans and Training Plans tailored to individual needs

Also with the colour of the icons in that app I want like a black base colour with gold accents if that would be possible

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
We update our app regularly to make it even better for you.

This release includes workout log updates:
- PDF viewer fixes
- image picker improvements
- bug fixes and improvements

Want something to make your life even easier in the app? Send a DM in the chat and we will pass it on to our developers to get sorted for you.
